1. Purpose

Lexicon Hound is the PantheonOS daemon responsible for semantic disambiguation and symbol routing.
It prevents meaning-collisions between:
	â€¢	PantheonOS symbols (mythic/architectural)
	â€¢	Real-world products or companies
	â€¢	Generic English terms
	â€¢	Symbols with dual technical + narrative referents

It ensures that terms like Pantheon, Forge, Garden, Oracle, Cathedral, etc. always map to the correct interpretation based on continuity, context, and registry lookup.

