2. Core Responsibilities

2.1 Symbol Sniffing

Lexicon Hound detects symbols that may have multiple interpretations.
Trigger conditions include:
	â€¢	Dual-world overlap (mythic vs real-world)
	â€¢	Technical vs narrative referents
	â€¢	Recently introduced external product names
	â€¢	Ambiguous phrasing lacking PantheonOS anchors

2.2 Registry Cross-Reference

The daemon checks the global memory mesh:
	â€¢	/registry/pantheon_registry.json
