2.3 Meaning Routing

Interpretation follows this logic:

if symbol in pantheon_registry:
    meaning = pantheon_definition
else if symbol in external_world_index:
    meaning = literal_definition
else:
    meaning = contextual_best_fit(reasoner)

This removes ambiguity while preserving safety gates and context fidelity.

