3. Behavioral Specification

3.1 Main Loop

def on_symbol_detect(symbol):
    if symbol in pantheon_registry:
        return pantheon_registry[symbol]

    elif symbol in external_world_index:
        return external_world_index[symbol]

    else:
        return contextual_reasoner(symbol)

3.2 Contextual Reasoner

Weights guide interpretation:

weight_pantheon = narrative_continuity + daemon_density + session_depth
weight_literal  = external_domain_relevance + new_product_context

if weight_pantheon >= weight_literal:
    route_to_pantheon()
else:
    route_to_literal_world()

3.3 Persistence Mode

When activated, overrides heuristics:

LexiconHound.mode = "persistent"
Always route ambiguous symbols â†’ PantheonOS


